CHECK:COMPARISON_TO_NULL: Comparison to NULL could be written "ops->cursor_src"
#113: FILE: drivers/video/console/softcursor.c:37:
+		if (ops->cursor_src != NULL)

Comparisons to NULL in the form (foo == NULL) or (foo != NULL)
are better written as (!foo) and (foo).

CHECK:SPACING: No space is necessary after a cast
#125: FILE: drivers/video/console/softcursor.c:48:
+	image = (struct fb_image *) (ops->cursor_src + dsize);

Whitespace style used in the kernel sources is described in kernel docs.

See: https://www.kernel.org/doc/html/latest/process/coding-style.html#spaces

